Posts.Content: I had my prostae removed on Sept. 13:04. I haven't gained eraction yet . I have used, Viagra , Cialis and even injected three times Coverjet impulse, once in clinic by doctor , at this time I had slight response but not enough to carry on further . Other two occassions injection was administered by my wife , who happened to be registered nurse. No response at all.
